===2020 census===
As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 census]], there were 57 people, 22 households, and 15 families residing in the city.<ref name="Census2020DP">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic Profile (DP1)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dp?get=NAME,DP1_0021P,DP1_0024P,DP1_0025C,DP1_0049C,DP1_0045C,DP1_0069C,DP1_0073C,DP1_0125P,DP1_0126P,DP1_0129P,DP1_0133P,DP1_0137P,DP1_0138P,DP1_0139P,DP1_0141P,DP1_0142P,DP1_0143P,DP1_0145P,DP1_0146P,DP1_0147C,DP1_0148C,DP1_0149C,DP1_0156C,DP1_0157C,DP1_0158C,DP1_0159P,DP1_0160P&for=place%3A06490&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref><ref name="Census2020PL">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Redistricting Data (Public Law 94-171)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/pl?get=NAME,P1_001N,P1_003N,P1_004N,P1_005N,P1_006N,P1_007N,P1_008N,P1_009N,P2_001N,P2_002N,H1_001N,H1_002N&for=place%3A06490&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2021|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref> All residents lived in rural areas.<ref name="Census2020DHC">{{cite web|title=2020 Decennial Census Demographic and Housing Characteristics (DHC)|url=https://api.census.gov/data/2020/dec/dhc?get=NAME,P2_002N,P2_003N&for=place%3A06490&in=state%3A19|website=United States Census Bureau|year=2023|access-date=May 1, 2026|df=mdy}}</ref> The [[population density]] was 126.3 inhabitants per square mile (48.8/km<sup>2</sup>). There were 25 housing units at an average density of 55.4 per square mile (21.4/km<sup>2</sup>).<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

Of the 22 households, 50.0% had children under the age of 18 living with them, 59.1% were [[Marriage|married-couple households]], 13.6% were cohabiting-couple households, 13.6% had a male householder with no spouse or partner present, and 13.6% had a female householder with no spouse or partner present.<ref name="Census2020DP"/> 31.8% of all households were non-families, 18.2% of all households were made up of individuals, and 9.1% had someone living alone who was 65 years old or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

There were 25 housing units, of which 12.0% were vacant. The homeowner vacancy rate was 0.0% and the rental vacancy rate was 0.0%.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

The median age in the city was 40.5 years. 19.3% of residents were under the age of 18, 22.8% were under the age of 20, 12.3% were between the ages of 20 and 24, 19.3% were from 25 to 44, 35.1% were from 45 to 64, and 10.5% were 65 years of age or older.<ref name="Census2020DP"/> The gender makeup of the city was 45.6% male and 54.4% female. For every 100 females there were 83.9 males, and for every 100 females age 18 and over there were 100.0 males age 18 and over.<ref name="Census2020DP"/>

